data.description: Welcome to this delightful home positioned on a spacious & private corner lot in Jerome, within walking distance to Camozzi Park & basketball courts.  With 1350 square feet of living space, this property is an excellent opportunity for resident buyers and investors alike.  Boasting three generously sized bedrooms, providing ample space for rest and relaxation. Natural light pours in through large windows, creating a welcoming ambiance in every room.  Step outside the double french back doors to the fully fenced backyard, a private retreat that has been thoughtfully landscaped with large bushes, and gravel areas. It's an ideal space for barbecues, gardening in your raised beds, or simply unwinding in a serene environment listening to your chickens clucking happily along.  Built in 1975, this home showcases the quality craftsmanship of its era while offering the opportunity for your personalization.  Garage was converted to a gym/bonus room.
